verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Thro’ days of toil, when heart doth fail, God will
take care of you;
When dangers fierce your path assail, God will take care of you.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}All you may need He will provide, God will take
Care of you.
Nothing you ask will be denied, God will take care of you.{/lang-eng}
